import React from 'react'; import { IGood } from '../models/models'; interface CatalogCardProps { good: IGood; } export function CatalogItem({ good }: CatalogCardProps) { return (
450 {`${good.type === 'volume' ? 'мл' : 'гр'}`}

{good.price} ₸
